{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}
{% block title %}Welcome to the Bakery{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
<div class="hero-section text-center d-flex flex-column justify-content-center align-items-center"
     style="background-image: url('{{ asset('image/hero-bakery.jpg') }}');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            height: 75vh;
            width: 100%;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;">
  <h1 class="fw-bold"
      style="color: #ffffffff; font-size: 7rem; text-shadow: 5px 5px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.88);">
    ABOUT US
  </h1>
  <p class="lead"
     style="color: #ffffffff; font-size: 4rem; text-shadow: 1px 20px 10px rgba(2, 2, 2, 0.5);">
    Come discover why we are City's favorite bakery.
  </p>
</div>



<div class="container py-5">
  <h2 class="text-center mb-4" style="font-size: 4.5rem; font-weight: bold;">Our Story</h2>
  <p class="text-center" style="font-size: 2rem; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
    Welcome to Sweetoria, where every bite tells a story!
Born from a passion for baking and creativity, Sweetoria started as a small kitchen dream in the heart of Dumaguete City. What began as a love for homemade pastries soon grew into a vision — to bring warmth, sweetness, and artistry into every celebration.

At Sweetoria, we blend tradition and technology. Our innovative online platform allows customers to customize their own cakes, order freshly baked pastries, and have them delivered right to their doorstep — all with a few taps. Whether it’s a birthday, wedding, or just a craving for something sweet, Sweetoria makes sure every moment is made extra special.

Our commitment goes beyond baking — we aim to create experiences worth sharing, powered by fresh ingredients, modern design, and heartfelt service. Because for us, it’s not just about cakes — it’s about creating happiness one sweet story at a time.
  </p>
</div>




{% endblock %}
